    <time_frame>Baseline to up to 4 weeks</time_frame>
    <description>For the biodistribution studies, regions of interest will be drawn on images of liver, kidney, bladder, heart, lung and blood pool to obtain regional activity count rates. Standardized uptake values (SUV = count activity per ml within region of interest (MBq-1)/(injected dose [MBq]/body weight [kgx1000]) will be calculated for different organs and for regions of tumor. Further, regional target to background count activity ratios will be established.</description>
